nt-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid #d1d1d1; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px;" src="https://www.ozchamp.com/upload/image/5-1-03.png" alt="" /></p>\n</div>\n<hr style="box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 21px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: #eeeeee; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both;" />\n<div class="col-md-12" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px;">\n<p class="text-vv-italic18 text-vv-border-left" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; border-left: 5px solid #ffbf00; padding-left: 10px;">步驟４－１：google search console &gt; 設定 &gt; 擁有權驗證</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid #d1d1d1; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px;" src="https://www.ozchamp.com/upload/image/5-1-04.png" alt="" /></p>\n</div>\n<hr style="box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 21px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: #eeeeee; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both;" />\n<div class="col-md-12" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px;">\n<p class="text-vv-italic18 text-vv-border-left" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; border-left: 5px solid #ffbf00; padding-left: 10px;">步驟４－２：google search console &gt; 設定 &gt; 擁有權驗證 &gt; Google Analytics(分析)</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid #d1d1d1; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px;" src="https://www.ozchamp.com/upload/image/5-1-05(1).png" alt="" /></p>\n</div>\n<hr style="box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 21px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: #eeeeee; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both;" />\n<div class="col-md-12" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px;">\n<p class="text-vv-italic18 text-vv-border-left" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; border-left: 5px solid #ffbf00; padding-left: 10px;">步驟４－３：google search console &gt; 設定 &gt; 擁有權驗證 &gt; Google Analytics(分析) &gt; 驗證</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;">完成驗證後，可回步驟二執行</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid #d1d1d1; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px;" src="https://www.ozchamp.com/upload/image/5-1-06.png" alt="" /></p>\n</div>\n<hr style="box-sizing: content-box; height: 0px; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 21px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: #eeeeee; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both;" />\n<div class="col-md-12" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; color: #777777; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', 微軟正黑體, Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px;">\n<p class="text-vv-italic18 text-vv-border-left" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal; font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; border-left: 5px solid #ffbf00; padding-left: 10px;">步驟５：確認是否連結成功(看是否有數據顯示）</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10.5px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-feature-settings: ''kern''; font-kerning: normal;"><img class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 3px solid #d1d1d1; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 0px;" src="https://www.ozchamp.com/upload/image/5-1-07.png" alt="" /></p>\n</div>', 5, '2022-08-18 08:19:10', '2022-08-18 08:19:10', NULL, 'Google Analytics 簡稱：GA是 Google 公司提供的免費數據分\n析工具，可用來查看即時在線訪客、分析訪客來源、訪客與網站\n的互動率、網站流量、關鍵字 ... 等報表功能。', 'Google Analytics 簡稱：GA是 Google 公司提供的免費數據分\n析工具，可用來查看即時在線訪客、分析訪客來源、訪客與網站\n的互動率、網站流量、關鍵字 ... 等報表功能。', NULL);

