(2, '香帥蛋糕｜台北人氣芋頭蛋糕店!團購推薦伴手禮蛋糕!', 6, '["Xjk55x6bkSot0JA9e9CxVxZDt1I45Q-metaMjAxNjExMjMwNzIyMTkuanBlZw==-.jpg","RJwpzfXIlBR7WgGLAjSLPwtaLQb0Yu-metaQTJfMTA4MC00NzB4NDcwLmpwZWc=-.jpg"]', 1, '香帥蛋糕對於產品的堅持，樸實原味的展現更彰顯其價值。台灣本土食材作為原料呈現獨特風味。蛋糕看似簡單卻保有四十年的堅持，用心著墨就像給自己家人享用一般。', '<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">口　　味</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">純天然芋泥（食品業者登錄字號：F-153226549-00000-9 投保產品責任險字號：富邦產物0525字第19AML0002556號）</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">特　　色</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">Q彈鬆軟的蛋糕體，搭配爆漿濃郁芋泥餡，紅遍全台灣的第一名芋卷！</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">商品規格</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">長 16cm / 寬 8cm / 高 8cm / 重量 850g</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">商品成份</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">芋頭、麵粉、大豆植物油、砂糖、牛奶、食鹽、雞蛋、可可粉（蛋奶素可食用）。</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">嘗鮮期限</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">請盡量於當天食用完畢。冷藏保存0-7℃以下，期限為收到商品日起算4天。</dd>\n</dl>\n<dl class="fck-packing" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: ''Roboto Condensed'', Roboto, DFPYuanLight-B5, 微软雅黑, 微軟正黑體, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; position: relative; color: #777777;">\n<dt style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2em 1em 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block; color: #333333; position: absolute;">保存方式</dt>\n<dd style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em 6em; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; zoom: 0; display: inline-block;">勿讓陽光直射或擺放於高溫處，常溫勿擺放超過3小時。若當天未食用完畢，請冷藏保存。</dd>\n</dl>', '<p>官網網址：<a href="https://www.scake.com.tw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.scake.com.tw/</a><br /><br /><iframe title="YouTube video player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Vz_cwOYrPOk" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>', 1, '2022-07-25 02:27:26', '2022-08-15 02:22:09', 99, '芋泥蛋糕,芋頭蛋糕', '香帥蛋糕對於產品的堅持，樸實原味的展現更彰顯其價值。台灣本土食材作為原料呈現獨特風味。蛋糕看似簡單卻保有四十年的堅持，用心著墨就像給自己家人享用一般。'),
(3, '想+舍計', 6, '["FosvoOrkiU0o4FfqS24aeWtuY1oUiK-meta5pyq5ZG95ZCNLTEuanBn-.jpg"]', 0, '想像居家的輪廓，是美好生活的期待， \n居處美適的家居，是生活的美感加值。', '<h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4"><span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; background-color: #ffffff;">想像居家的輪廓，是美好生活的期待，居處美適的家居，是生活的美感加值。 一杯好茶、好咖啡 聊聊生活的想法、家的線條 為您構思打造 適切需求的居家空間， 讓您回到起居的住所，看到生活的美好。 想+舍計主要從事室內空間設計，將舒適的溫度注入您家的空間，打造怡然舒適的居家天地。 如果您有任何空間設計、系統家具、廚具櫥櫃的需求，歡迎您與我們連繫，我們將竭誠的為您服務。</span></h4>', '<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;">想像居家的輪廓，是美好生活的期待，&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;">居處美適的家居，是生活的美感加值。</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;">一杯好茶、好咖啡</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;">聊聊生活的想法、家的線條</span></p>\n<p><span style="color: #6b7280; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoj